tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE suppliers (
    supplier_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    supplier_name VARCHAR(50),
    contact_person VARCHAR(50),
    email_address VARCHAR(50),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20),
    pricing_agreement_id INT,
    product_catalog_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE suppliers (
  supplier_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  supplier_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  contact_person_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  contact_email VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  contact_phone VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE products (
  product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  product_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  supplier_id UUID REFERENCES suppliers(supplier_id),
  price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  in_stock BOOLEAN NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE suppliers (
  supplier_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  supplier_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  contact_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  email VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  phone_number VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE pricing_agreements (
  agreement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  supplier_id INT NOT NULL,
  product_id INT NOT NULL,
  unit_price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  CONSTRAINT fk_supplier_id FOREIGN KEY (supplier_id) REFERENCES suppliers(supplier_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Suppliers (
    supplier_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    supplier_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    contact_name VARCHAR(255),
    contact_email VARCHAR(255),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE PricingAgreements (
    agreement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    supplier_id INT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    agreement_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE ProductCatalog (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    supplier_id INT,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE,
    status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
  product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  supplier_id INT,
  price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (supplier_id) REFERENCES suppliers(supplier_id)
);

CREATE TABLE order_items (
  order_item_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  order_id INT,
  product_id INT,
  quantity INT NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (order_id) REFERENCES orders(order_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(product_id)
);

CREATE TABLE pricing_agreements (
  agreement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  supplier_id INT,
  start_date DATE NOT NULL,
  agreement_details VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (supplier_id) REFERENCES suppliers(supplier_id)
);
